description: Manage VPN server configuration IPSec policies.

commands.name: az network vpn-server-config ipsec-policy add
commands.summary: Add an IPSec policy to a VPN server configuration.

commands.name: az network vpn-server-config ipsec-policy list
commands.summary: List VPN server configuration IPSec policies.

commands.name: az network vpn-server-config ipsec-policy remove
commands.summary: Remove an IPSec policy from a VPN server configuration.

commands.name: az network vpn-server-config ipsec-policy wait
commands.summary: Place the CLI in a waiting state until a condition of the IPSec policy of a VPN server configuration is met.
